### Install "REST Client" extension in VSCode, then click "Send Request"

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Generate a Book (main pipeline)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Luna and the Magic Forest",
  "theme": "A small bunny named Luna discovers a glowing mushroom that leads her to a hidden fairy village",
  "page_count": 4,
  "age_range": "6-9",
  "art_style": "standard",
  "character_name": "Luna"
}

###

### List My Books (gallery)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Single Book
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/books/REPLACE_WITH_BOOK_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Photo Upload (Phase 2 - returns 501)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/photos/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
